item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Once Upon a Time TV Show Music (QueenCordy)
item.description:
Hello,

I know this is a long shot but there is a YouTube poster by the name of QueenCordy who posted the unreleased music from the TV show Once Upon a Time. QueenCordy had them uploaded via Meguploads but they are down now and one of them needs a decryption key. I tried to reach out to QueenCordy on Twitter but they restricted contacted.

Did anyone manage to get all of this music? Can you pretty please upload it? I highly doubt QueenCordy released it in a lossless format but if you have it, that would be wonderful.

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfxf9wbRcOelvEQCE0kx-ajhttjrjW-Wt
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfxf9wbRcOem3lC9k7n6b_if3mg_Q7awe

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfxf9wbRcOel8qbnhdjmvTeL73RMxVk1X
